Author: Joel Barnes <j@barnzilla.ca> [aut, cre], 
	Michelle Guerrero <mguerrero@cheo.on.ca> [aut]
Maintainer: Joel Barnes <j@barnzilla.ca>
Description: This package contains tools to compute CAPL-2
    (Canadian Assessment of Physical Literacy, Second Edition;
    www.capl-eclp.ca) scores and interpretations from raw data, and tools 
	to visualize the results.
